<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Ye Xie and Liz McCormick h=
ave sort of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/314274=
29.263436/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtM=
